text: Nail Narimanovich Mukhamedyarov () is a Soviet weightlifter. He won a Silver medal in the 90 kg class at the 1988 Summer Olympics in Seoul. == References == Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:People from Andijan Region Category:Soviet male weightlifters Category:Uzbekistani male weightlifters Category:Olympic weightlifters of the Soviet Union Category:Weightlifters at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic silver medalists for the Soviet Union Category:Olympic medalists in weightlifting Category:Medalists at the 1988 Summer Olympics
